WHY after THREE YEARS of live development is it still possible to zonecrash into Great Divide, Skyshrine, Greig's End, Shadowhaven, and Dawnshroud with approximately 33-40% frequency?  Do you folks over there at Verant know how unprofessional that makes you all look?  That is a MAJOR annoyance, please please please do something about these zones...</font>
			
